{"tid":2362144,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 十勝咖哩日式炸魚飯","createTime":"2021-01-11T08:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T09:28:04.000Z","uid":116775,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"294d0e03f2f5db99c9dd97bab078d1650df182ce","tid":2362144,"uid":116775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mhQjAq7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmhQjAq7.jpg&h=36647b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n價錢：$75 (下午茶八五折) <br />\n<br />\n味道：暫時香港食過最正嘅日式午市定食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n炸魚好嫩滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身幾驚佢會炸到茶記斑塊咁，原來佢又滑又有啲魚味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咖喱普通正常，算多蔬菜，幾有口感<br />\n<br />\n個餐仲包好多配菜，有茶碗蒸、刺身、水果、漬物、沙律同味噌湯<br />\n<br />\n茶碗蒸個庭有真&middot;蟹肉同蝦，加埋巧巧食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n刺身竟然唔係 cheap cheap，薄到喊嗰種，係肥美嘅三文魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個漬物係味噌蒜頭，但好神奇，佢一啲都唔辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nstaff 服務都好好 <br />\n<br />\n感覺搞手只求打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結：成餐食落橫隔膜巧 C 服<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2062f06a1651d5c90884351782fb7b989a178724","tid":2362144,"uid":195046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32964420ffef1b30221b34e9f792162035d3840c","tid":2362144,"uid":75311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:54:59.000Z","msg":"好餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119ee70af27a49db95daf9bac915a368ea836af9","tid":2362144,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"2062f06a1651d